Known bugs in the current version of gEdit:

	* Occasionally crashes when you open eight or more files at a time.

	* Changes to the font will not take effect until gEdit is restarted.
	  
	* The line number indicator is basically smashed, and the column
	  indicator isn't so accurate.
	  
	* If you try to print a new (Untitled) file, gEdit will sigsegv. (Save
	  the file before printing)

	

